# f5distributedcloud_tunnel (Data Source)

The `f5distributedcloud_tunnel` data source retrieves information about an existing tunnel.

## Example Usage

```hcl
data "f5distributedcloud_tunnel" "example" {
  name      = "my-tunnel"
  namespace = "my-namespace"
}

output "tunnel_type" {
  value = data.f5distributedcloud_tunnel.example.tunnel_type
}
```



<!-- schema generated by tfplugindocs -->
## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) Name of the tunnel to look up.
- `namespace` (String) Namespace where the tunnel is located.

### Read-Only

- `description` (String) Description of the tunnel.
- `id` (String) Unique identifier of the tunnel.
- `tunnel_type` (String) Type of tunnel (IPSEC, SSL).
